title: Show HN: Plant trees while you sleep
text:
How I used Spotify to plant 14,000 trees.

A year ago I uploaded a short (31 sec) audio clip to Spotify. Its streaming royalties go towards tree planting.

So far it's been streamed 1.4 million times and we've donated 14,000 trees.

Now we're expanding to white, brown and pink noise. You can play it in the background while you work, study or sleep.

I like to have background noise on while I sleep.

It blocks out distractions.

Streaming for about 2 hours will plant 1 tree

So an 8 hour sleep will plant around 4 trees. A good excuse for a lie-in

Check it out at www.mptr.ee

Ask HN: Where should I host my email
text:
I know guys we had several discussions about this in the past, but here's the thing:

Premise: I want to use my own domain for my private emails. I am not brave enough to host my own mailserver. Conclusion: I purchased webhosting incl. email server from a EU based company where DKIM and SPF are properly configured.

So far so good, worked for quite some time, but now:

Problem 1: (more severe): more and more of my sent emails go to the recipients spam folder, this seems especially true for large providers such as gmail.

Problem 2 (can handle locally, more of an annoyance): incoming spam is increasing as the webproviders spamassin doesnt seem to work quite well.

So my question is this: Where should I host my email to maximize acceptance of sent mails by major mailservers?

Show HN: macOS Live coin tracker (BTC, ETH and others)
text:
Hi HN!

I recently started to follow my dreams and become an Indie Maker and decided to start with something useful and minimal with time of development to get experience with packaging and promoting a product.

A menu bar application that updates cryptocurrencies (BTC, ETH & others) prices in real-time and allows users to create alerts for price changes. Pricing data is updated every minute. CryptoBar lets you easily display and monitor the prices of your favorite cryptocurrencies directly from your Mac menu bar.

Features

- Minimalistic design - Support multiple crypto currencies - Auto launch at login
